<br>
2. I could see myself in both of her side mirrors (back window was dark tint, couldn't tell) as I came up on her. Keep in mind; I am a full size white Explorer, this is broad daylight-no clouds, the speed limit on this road is 35mph and I was going 35-40, the road is straight-you can see a good 6 half mile street lights looking north or south.<br>
<br>
